column1: Specifications: "Compact UniFi Console with full UniFi application support and a pre-installed 1TB HDD for NVR storage."
Optional USB-C power with Quick Charge 2.0/3.0 compliant adapter only
Includes full UniFi application suite for device management

"Hard drive capacity": "1 TB 2.5\" SATA HDD (user-upgradeable*)\n* The Cloud Key Gen2 Plus only supports hard drives that can operate on 5V power. Hard drives that require additional power are not supported."
"Ambient operating temperature": "0 to 35° C (32 to 104° F)"
